The paper discusses the construction of an operational multi-domain networked infrastructure-as-a-service (NIaaS) testbed, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of semantic web technologies for managing resources, which could fall under the categories of data management (cs.DB) and software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper discusses the integration of network provisioning functions, which could fall under the category of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) and computer engineering (cs.CE).
